  For the research project, this is essential for mapping the hermeneutic position alongside
  conservative and critical approaches. Ambord's focus on political implications also directly
  addresses how philosophical concepts of tradition connect to political theory.

  POSITION: Hermeneutic philosophy (Gadamer). Tradition as enabling condition of understanding
