  RELEVANCE: Offers systematic comparison of the two major positions in the tradition-reason debate. Useful for seeing how the Habermas-Gadamer disagreement concerns not just epistemology but also authority, legitimacy, and the grounds for political critique. Helps clarify what separates critical theory from hermeneutics and what common ground might exist.

